Application Development
=======================
1 creating birthday remainder application using spring boot.
2 I am using below end points for the application.
    To add friends: "/add"
    To retrive all DOB information: "/all"
    To delete friends : "/delete"
3 using tymeleaf I will develop frontend of the application
4 My-SQL DB for data storing
5 To update friend "/updateFriend"

Application deployment in docker
========================
1. shell script file for building the application
2. shell script file for running the docker container
3. shell script file for cron job as per requirement
